        "short": "Easily export YouTube comments and analyze them with AI, so you can find potential products and apps ideas.",
        "full": "Easily export YouTube comments and analyze them with AI, so you can find potential products and apps ideas.\n\nWhy install it:\n\n- Save time: Pull comments into CSV, JSON, or a TXT layout suited for analysis instead of copying threads by hand.\n- Flexible export: Download files, copy all to the clipboard, or open the payload in Claude or ChatGPT (your account on those sites).\n- Bulk workflow: download comments from multiple videos at once\nHistory: Recent exports help you revisit past runs.\n\nHow to use it:\n- Open a YouTube watch page\n- Click on the extension’s button\n- Click on \"Fetch Comments\" \n- Export or open in your preferred tool.\n\nNote\nClaude and ChatGPT are third-party services; this extension prepares and transfers text for you to use on those sites under your login. It is not affiliated with Google, YouTube, Anthropic, or OpenAI."
