      "slug": "claude-limit-monitor",
      "chromeExtensionId": "mljfhcfnjbfibedpiaheeihpbjajfcal",
      "name": "Claude Limit Monitor: Track Free Usage & When Limit Resets",
      "icon": "⚡",
      "chromeExtensionIcon": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/3cYDG58PPLTqHaniw459Hj1o8YoOOThKCHK6BLIOaUTL4Vir0AjOj0KwJCS0u41XMhkXs7VMPdUdJ_3puuN41Eqq",
      "tagline": "Monitor your Claude.ai usage in real time. See how much free usage you have left and when your limit resets.",
      "status": "live",
      "price": "Free",
      "revenue": "$0",
      "chromeStoreUrl": "https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/mljfhcfnjbfibedpiaheeihpbjajfcal",
      "version": "1.0.02",
      "lastUpdated": "2026-06-06",
      "category": "Productivity",
      "platform": "Google Chrome",
      "description": {
        "short": "Have you ever hit Claude's usage limit mid-conversation and had no idea it was coming? Or spent time looking for when exactly your allowance resets so you can get back to work?",
        "full": "Have you ever hit Claude's usage limit mid-conversation and had no idea it was coming? Or spent time looking for when exactly your allowance resets so you can get back to work? \n\nNot anymore!\n\nWHAT IT DOES\nClaude Limit Monitor adds a small status bar to claude.ai showing exactly how much of your usage allowance you've used and when it resets. It's extremely lightweight and runs exclusively on the Claude.ai website, ensuring that it doesn't slow down your browsing experience.\n\nYou can see your current session limit, your weekly limit, and a countdown to the next reset, all while you chat. \n\nYou can also turn on a desktop notification so Chrome pings you the moment your limit refreshes.\n\nWHO IS THIS FOR\nAnyone who uses Claude regularly and has ever been caught off guard by a usage limit. Especially useful if you rely on Claude for work and need to plan around reset times.\n\nHOW DOES IT WORK\n1. Go to Claude.ai \n2. You should see the widget above your chat box. \n3. (optional) click on the Chrome Extension popup to change options as per your needs.\n\nIS IT FREE?\n100%. No trial, no paywall, no premium tier.\n\nIS IT SECURE?\n100% private. It only runs on claude.ai, reads usage data that's already on the page, and sends nothing anywhere. No accounts, no tracking, no data collection of any kind.\n\nFEEDBACK, BUGS OR QUESTIONS?\nCodedCitadel@gmail.com"
      },
